name: HEATHEN
description:
My people were purged from their lands, the underworld of the unholy had gone merciless while I walked weak, broken into my world seeking some kind of power. humans brutally murdered while I was left tortured lying in my pool of blood, but the rain ah.. it washes away all the sins this city has EVER SEEN, I FELT like a spec of this filth, dripping into the gutters of nothingness. 
As darkness shadows the hope we HARBOR, freedom has become sacred. The cries will not go undone for a heathen I have become...
